parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to stall when coming to a stop, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders or stalls when coming to a stop
often accompanied by warning lights on the dashboard. The engine may die
and the vehicle may need to be restarted.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls when coming to a stop
the engine stalls when turning
the engine stalls when shifting into reverse
the engine shudders and dies
the vehicle vibrates and shutters abnormally
the engine stalls on inclines
the engine stalls when braking abruptly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The torque converter does not shut off properly
causing the vehicle to stall periodically
the wheel locks up while turning
the vehicle stalls on the highway.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine misfiring can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine misfires
causing the vehicle to stall
the engine misfires
causing the vehicle to shudder and die
the check engine light goes on
causing the brake
traction
and cruise lights to flash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the head gasket can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The head gasket blows
causing coolant to back up and vent
the coolant leaks
affecting the function of the brakes and power steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or death, and the inability to complete recall repairs in a timely manner can leave vehicles on the road with potentially deadly defects.
symptoms: Airbag light on
open circuit found
airbag failure to deploy in accidents
inability to complete recall repairs due to parts unavailability.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Parts Distribution Disconnect and Delayed Recall Repairs
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts for recall repairs can lead to delayed or incomplete repairs, leaving vehicles on the road with potentially deadly defects.
symptoms: Parts unavailability
delayed recall repairs
inability to complete repairs due to parts distribution issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Failure to Deploy in Accidents
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag failure to deploy in accidents
resulting in injuries or fatalities.
